{"tid":189377,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇試過發清醒夢？","createTime":"2017-04-06T11:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T12:21:16.000Z","uid":100082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4bab565185e06903412be75382e30f8769dd2d6","tid":189377,"uid":100082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:24:31.000Z","msg":"我發過幾次，但唔知嗰d算唔算係清醒夢<br />\n<br />\n通常發嘅時係係已經訓醒，但繼續攤係床到，攤攤下再訓番嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n開始嘅時候半夢半醒嘅，跟住就會感覺到頭皮發麻同好嘈，但果種嘈唔係耳邊聽到，而係類似腦入面發出黎咁<br />\n<br />\n跟住就會全身郁唔到，入左夢境，但意識上好清楚自己發緊夢，而且可以控制自己夢境內容嘅<br />\n<br />\n但有時就會全身郁唔到加埋感覺唔到自己呼吸緊，要呼吸得好特登，成日驚自己呼吸唔到會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家有冇類似經驗？一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02059191e4d2507b758509932c57e35e605a989","tid":189377,"uid":102630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"有.但無試郁所以唔知郁唔郁到"},{"pid":"39ddd8785ca3e5696aae45ec707b9f61e5979cb8","tid":189377,"uid":100082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有.但無試郁所以唔知郁唔郁到</blockquote><br />\n巴打都係會覺得頭皮發麻同好嘈？<br />\n我成日都諗究竟我係靈魂出竅定純屬個身訓著左所以郁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3239ef184f975893cb3ac34302d76722c5c3c9","tid":189377,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"你講個樣似比鬼責多D, 清醒夢唔係應該控制到自己個種?"},{"pid":"f7962dc98b28aad53f5bc76b1c82b550a60c9000","tid":189377,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講個樣似比鬼責多D, 清醒夢唔係應該控制到自己個種?</blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 我睇啲唔睇啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}